DTEND;TZID=GMT 标准时间:20260407T140000
CLASS:PUBLIC
DESCRIPTION:Dear all\,\n\n \n\n感谢各位的大力支持，D Talent Prog
 ram 2026 Q1季度交流会完美收官。约个会，现场讨论下项目
 激励如何分配。谢谢！\n\n \n\n下附为最终结果和补充信
 息，附件为评分细节表。\n\n \n\n\n\n \n\n\n\n \n\n\n\nBest Regar
 ds\,\n\nLily Liu\n\n \n\n_________________________________________________
 _______________________________\n\nMicrosoft Teams meeting \n\nJoin: https
 ://teams.microsoft.com/meet/35388594589159?p=NwppDc37vEzOr51LTP <https://t
 eams.microsoft.com/meet/35388594589159?p=NwppDc37vEzOr51LTP>  \n\nMeeting 
 ID: 353 885 945 891 59 \n\nPasscode: ni62FW76 \n\n________________________
 ________\n\nNeed help? <https://aka.ms/JoinTeamsMeeting?omkt=en-US>  | Sys
 tem reference <https://teams.microsoft.com/l/meetup-join/19%3ameeting_NjE2
 MTQzZGItNTA4Ny00YzA4LWE0NjAtNTM5ZDRhNTQyYjli%40thread.v2/0?context=%7b%22T
 id%22%3a%228d4b558f-7b2e-40ba-ad1f-e04d79e6265a%22%2c%22Oid%22%3a%221e3fea
 23-7c50-4fb2-a71b-c28eb213e712%22%7d>  \n\nFor organizers: Meeting options
  <https://teams.microsoft.com/meetingOptions/?organizerId=1e3fea23-7c50-4f
 b2-a71b-c28eb213e712&tenantId=8d4b558f-7b2e-40ba-ad1f-e04d79e6265a&threadI
 d=19_meeting_NjE2MTQzZGItNTA4Ny00YzA4LWE0NjAtNTM5ZDRhNTQyYjli@thread.v2&me
 ssageId=0&language=en-US>  \n\nPrivacy and security <https://filehub.admir
 alcloud.com/dl/5/d6981e10-1775-44b3-92cf-aaf920ff7119>  \n\n______________
 __________________________________________________________________\n\n \n\
 n \n\n_____________________________________________\nFrom: Liu\, Xin06 \nS
 ent: Friday\, March 20\, 2026 8:42 AM\nTo: Jia\, Xiaoge <xiaoge.jia@beneck
 e-changshun.com.cn>\; Tian\, Richard <ming.tian@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\
 ; Yang\, Laraine <liping.yang@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\nCc: Sun\, Juan <j
 uan.sun@benecke-changshun.com.cn>\; Xue\, Jialei <jialei.xue@benecke-chang
 shun.com.cn>\nSubject: Budget Proposal for the D Talent Program Award\n\n 
 \n\nDear all\,\n\n \n\nFor information only\; a formal e‑sign will follo
 w shortly. Thank you!\n\n \n\nThis award recognizes teams and individuals 
 who have demonstrated outstanding performance in the D Talent Program. The
  final recipients will be determined through a group voting process on Mar
 ch 26\, 2026.\n\nWe request budget allocation to support this award\, cove
 ring the planned cash incentives for the selected recipients. The awards w
 ill be paid together with payroll\, charged to Cost Center 43100 and Accou
 nt K40702\, with taxes withheld collectively.\n\n \n\nThis budget will ena
 ble us to:\n\n*  Recognize and reward outstanding contributions\n\n*  Enco
 urage team engagement and high-quality project delivery\n\n*  Promote best
  practices and experience sharing across the D Talent Program\n\n \n\nBest
  regards\,\n\n \n\nLily Liu(Liu Xin)\n\nME Engineer BCZ\n\nContiTech Surfa
 ce Solutions\n\n \n\nMobile: +86 189 5113 2980\n\nE-mail: xin.6.liu@beneck
 e-changshun.com.cn <mailto:xin.6.liu@benecke-changshun.com.cn> \n\nWebsite
 : www.continental-industry.com <http://www.continental-industry.com/> \n\n
  \n
