 monthly%20review%20meeting?csf=1&web=1&e=9yVbg9>  in advance. For project\
 , pls. prepare A3 report\, for JDI\, pls. prepare project one-pager.\n\n \
 n\nThank you.\n\n \n\nBest Regards\,\n\nFiona Huang\n\n \n
